# **"Send thanks" feature on Workplace**

At JTI, we would like to start using this feature, but since there is no option to extract reports/stats, we don't really see the benefit of using it, since from an admin/P&C point of view, we can't really know who have been recognized by their colleagues.

@workplace team > is it something you plan to improve (short-term)?

@all community > how do you use this feature?

Thank you in advance for your answers üôè

Hiüëãüèª,

I am looking to exchange on the implementation of Workplace in a manufacturing environment with unionize or hourly employees. Anyone can share best practices? 

I would like more precisely to build the right strategy for this population. 
These are the factors that i have to deal with:
Hourly employees should have the main focus on operations;
Manufacturing employees are not necessarily in touch with digital tool;
Every hour spent on a task have to be paid;
They are not use to be connected with office people;
They usually don't have access to communications if it is not from their supervisor.

I see an amazing opportunity with Workplace to connect them and I hope to leverage it but with all these constraints, I want to make sure, we get it right!

Let me know if you can help or share your experience! 
Thanks
Val
